Ahold Plans 1 Billion Euro Buyback Program, Lifts Dividend by 26 Percent

-- B y   C e l e s t e   P e r r i
-- 
2011-03-03T05:53:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/ahold-plans-1-billion-euro-buyback-program-lifts-dividend-by-26-percent.html
Royal Ahold NV said it plans to
start a 1 billion-euro buyback program and increased its
dividend by 26 percent to 29 cents a share.  The buyback will run for the next 18 months, the Amsterdam-
based company said in a statement today. The company also
repeated its mid-term targets for sales growth of 5 percent and
an underlying retail operating margin of  5 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at 
 cperri@bloomberg.net  